                <h1>Chris Christie: A Brief Biography</h1>
                <p>Chris Christie, born September 6, 1962, in Newark, New Jersey, is an American politician and attorney. He served as the 55th governor of New Jersey from 2010 to 2018. A member of the Republican Party, Christie gained national attention for his leadership during Hurricane Sandy and his candidacy in the 2016 presidential race.</p>
